briefdescription.para: Pricing engine for compound options using analytical formulae.

detaileddescription.para: The formulas are taken from "Foreign Exchange Risk", Uwe Wystup, Risk 2002, where closed form Greeks are available. (not available in Haug 2007). Value: Page 84, Greeks: Pages 94-95.

xrefdescription.para: the correctness of the returned value is tested by reproducing results available in literature.
